				  -=+=- bitweaver -=+=-

Welcome to bitweaver! A Powerful, flexible, simple, and fast web framework and
content management system

DOCUMENTATION

* It is highly recommended you refer to the online documentation at
* http://www.bitweaver.org

INSTALLATION

* point your browser to the install/install.php file. 
* There are no shell scripts or other evil things.

